text: a l laoh minban bangkeut samreab mnoussa mneak aoy mean behdaung pir nowknong khluon robsa ke laey . haey trong minban chattouk phriyea puok anak del puok anak thveu hsai heur puok neang noh chea mdeay robsa puok anak laey . haey trong min chattouk kaunchenhchum robsa puok anakchea kaunobangkeut robsa puok anak laey . teangnoh kuchea peakyasaamdei del chenhpi meat robsa puok anak bonnaoh . te a l laoh mean bantoul pit ning changaoulobangheanh meakra del troemotrauv
